    • Constructor Detail

      • XmlSubstitution

        public XmlSubstitution(XmlDataWorkspace ws,
                       XmlDataElementTag... list)
        Specify the head of a substitution group and its members. The first item in the list is the head. The remaining items are the members. All members XmlElements must already exist when this method is called. The head XmlElement must not already exist when this method is called.
        Parameters:
        ws - the XmlDataWorkspace
        list - the head and member list specified using XmlDataElementTags.
        See Also:
        XmlDataWorkspace.wrapper(XmlDataElementTag, boolean)
